I am proud to have secured over $3 million of federal transit funds to reconstruct the remaining 4,100 feet of paved runway at the Brownsville/South Padre Island International Airport (BRO).

This funding will help the airport grow and operate more smoothly to better serve our growing community!

Unless Congress acts, tax credits that help South Texans afford health care will expire. Premiums will soar and many in our region will lose care altogether.

I am committed to working across the aisle to ensure that does not happen. Seniors, veterans and families deserve access to affordable high quality health care!

Without congressional action to extend these tax credits, South Texans who obtain health care through the ACA will be forced to pay almost 200% more in insurance costs.

Its time for Republicans to right their wrongs, and do right by the American people.

I am proud to join my Democratic colleagues in co-sponsoring the Protecting Healthcare and Lowering Costs Act of 2025. Through this bill, we would reverse the drastic health care cuts Republicans passed in the “Big, Ugly Bill” and permanently extend the Affordable Care Act’s (ACA) enhanced premium tax credits.
